{"type": "article", "id": 27627, "title": "玻璃与大理石的组合花器", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-01T06:57:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 108, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021519330LzDlbqZQTmRCYwh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>来自斯德歌尔摩的 <a href=\"http://studioeo.se/\">Studio EO</a> 最近推出了一组名为 Indefinite Vases 的花器。经过精心设计而吹制成的玻璃容器就像是慵懒地或坐或躺在大理石制成的底座上一样，强调了空间与物体之间的关系。坚硬的石块与易碎的玻璃经过组合，带给人一种奇妙的美感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151930Qk0s6P31jdYwCASG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151931YMp59OZWkx7jt1Pv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151932u0SxDkiLH6Xmv9V8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151932WTL8C9MZlPg5dqv4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}